{"tid":716924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"𠝹刀色魔迫15歲女拍裸照","createTime":"2018-06-25T16:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T16:49:50.000Z","uid":1749,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e7af4e6177fea9b1c1a26da7eb2c32612b088f76","tid":716924,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:17:04.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】入伙僅半年的荔枝角新落成公屋海麗昨晚發生駭人風化案。一名十五歲女童返家時，在大廈內遭遇「𠝹刀色魔」，女童被對方用𠝹刀挾持，拖往後樓梯大肆非禮後，色魔更脫去她全身衣服，然後用繩索綑綁，拍下多張裸照。警方接報後封鎖全幢大廈，並出動警犬搜捕色魔，但無發現。<br />\n<br />\n獨自乘搭電梯出事<br />\n警方事後將受害女童送往法醫鑑證科檢驗，並取走她的衣服化驗。鑑證科人員今日凌晨仍在案發現場後樓梯蒐集證物，並取走大廈閉路電視影帶調查。警方表示，案中色魔年約二十餘歲，身高五呎八吋，身材瘦削，案發時頭戴黑色帽，身穿深藍色恤衫及深色長褲。 <br />\n警方消息稱，昨晚七時許，一名十五歲女童外出返家，獨自一人乘搭電梯上樓，但當她離開電梯時，在住所對開走廊被一名男子箍頸挾持，並被人拖往後樓梯非禮。 <br />\n消息稱，事主雖曾極力反抗，但色魔孔武有力，並亮出刀威嚇，結果被對方制服。女童慘遭淫辱後，更被對方強行剝去全身衣服，並用繩索綑綁，其後，色魔用相機拍下女童多張裸照。色魔清理現場後沿樓梯逃去。女童跑回家中，向父親哭訴，父親連忙報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員封鎖大廈調查<br />\n警員到場後將整幢大廈封鎖，並召來警犬，在大廈逐層樓搜索，至今晨零時許仍無發現。案中女童身體無表面傷痕，警方稍後安排她接受法醫檢驗。 <br />\n警方事後取走案發現場大廈的出入登記資料，初步懷疑案中的「刀色魔」是一名慣犯。警方根據事主提供的資料，通令各警區追緝其下落。 <br />\n發生風化案的海麗今年初陸續入伙，目前約住有三千三百戶共一萬名居民，屬甲級保安公屋。"},{"pid":"6ed939fa7c0c8051a527d767b89ab0ab6828d181","tid":716924,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:17:09.000Z","msg":"拉到人未？"},{"pid":"b12c03e82a84d3906be2d854bbd28abc86d11885","tid":716924,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"回撚夠帶未"},{"pid":"a486d0f9947e694ce638a92290b6707d315002c2","tid":716924,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"2017年12月28日"},{"pid":"63c900811e70d36d091cd391e8da7022ff6e3549","tid":716924,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a486d0f9947e694ce638a92290b6707d315002c2","tid":716924,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"2017年12月28日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"屌quote錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de44942501d03507cbfccb44823593f1baf6a3d2","tid":716924,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:23:41.000Z","msg":"都冇扑野 又冇受傷<br />\n<br />\n好小事姐<br />\n<br />\n小事化無啦 咪又係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c7db654d6fa908201ca6eda4e74d13106b0c6e","tid":716924,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"昨晚七時許... 咁撚早都落手，咁撚狼.."},{"pid":"d7fb1736fdedf3f21f3ab83709eb238f01c9341c","tid":716924,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"63c900811e70d36d091cd391e8da7022ff6e3549","tid":716924,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a486d0f9947e694ce638a92290b6707d315002c2","tid":716924,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"2017年12月28日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"屌quote錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20050706/5027113\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20050706%2F5027113&d=2FcVU8aJTYe%2BL66XBXzPh5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=282928c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20050706%2F502711